###############################################################################
##                                                                           ##
##         Makefile for FreeRTOS associated with ECA-MSI on SCU-LM32         ##
##                                                                           ##
##---------------------------------------------------------------------------##
## File:    FreeRTOS/Demo/SCU_LM32_GCC/rtosEcaMsiTest/Makefile               ##
